---
title: Chinese Style Chicken Noodles with Green Beans and Pak Choi
description: This delicious Chinese Style Chicken Noodles has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.

Due to quality issues with Bell Pepper, you'll instead receive Pak Choi. As such, the recipe photos are slightly different to what your dish will look like. Don't worry, we've updated the instructions so it'll still be just as delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R24_W19_UK_FR1895-30_Main_low-e92242f7.jpg
